import env from '../../../common/js/env'
import conf from '../conf'

export default function path () {
  let origin = window.sessionStorage.getItem('origin_host') || conf.domain
  const o = env().originHost(origin)
  let projectName = conf.api
  // const app = 'app'
  const path = {
    home_info: `${o}/${projectName}/app/home/home_info`, // [home, verify_result] 首页信息 审核状态
    get_certification_status: `${o}/${projectName}/auth/get_certification_status`, // [verify] 认证状态
    user_query: `${o}/${projectName}/auth/user_query`,
    pre_audit: `${o}/${projectName}/auth/pre_audit`, // [verify] 认证页的提交申请
    get_order_detail: `${o}/${projectName}/app/loan/get_user_order_detail`, // [verify] 获取订单详情
    verify_location: `${o}/${projectName}/auth/verify_location`, // [verify] 上传用户定位
    get_market_info: `${o}/${projectName}/app/market/get_market_business_info`, // [verify_result] 贷超入口
    get_apply_basic: `${o}/${projectName}/auth/get_apply_basic`, // [basic] 基本信息回显
    // apply: `${o}/${projectName}/auth/apply`, // [basic] 提交基本信息
    apply_info: `${o}/${projectName}/auth/apply_info`, // [basic] 提交基本信息
    get_contact_info: `${o}/${projectName}/auth/get_contact_info`, // [contact] 联系人信息回显
    save_contact_info: `${o}/${projectName}/auth/save_contact_info`, // [contact] 联系人信息提交
    get_certified_info: `${o}/${projectName}/auth/get_certified_info`, // [sign, loan_protocol] 身份信息
    face_recognize: `${o}/${projectName}/faceid/face_recognize`, // [loan_application] 人脸识别
    get_order_status: `${o}/${projectName}/app/loan/get_order_status`, // 获取审核状态（用于轮询状态）
    // other
    agreement_list: `${o}/${projectName}/app/agreement/get_list`, // [protocol] 协议
    get_pic_url: `${o}/${projectName}/app/agreement/get_pic_url`, // [protocol_contain] 协议图片
    get_user_all_equity: `${o}/${projectName}/app/equity/get_user_all_equity`, // [history] 历史权益
    get_order_equity: `${o}/${projectName}/app/equity/get_order_equity`, // [right] 权益
    get_equity: `${o}/${projectName}/app/equity/get_equity`, // [right，history] 权益
    loan_apply: `${o}/${projectName}/app/loan/loan_apply`, // [loan_application] 借款申请页面数据接口
    loan_apply_callback: `${o}/${projectName}/app/loan/loan_apply_callback`, // [loan_application] 借款申请回调接口
    get_agreement_data: `${o}/${projectName}/app/agreement/get_agreement_data`, // [loan_application] 合同编号
    get_contract_info: `${o}/${projectName}/app/loan/get_contract_info`, // [loan_protocol] 借款协议

    create_escrow_account: `${o}/${projectName}/app/Bankcard/create_escrow_account`, // 绑卡相关 [ bank ]
    get_escrow_info: `${o}/${projectName}/app/bankcard/get_escrow_info`, // 绑卡相关 [ bank ]
    rebind_bankcard: `${o}/${projectName}/app/bankcard/rebind_bankcard`,
    unbind_bankcard: `${o}/${projectName}/app/bankcard/unbind_bankcard`,
    get_user_info: `${o}/${projectName}/bank_Card/get_user_info`, // 身份信息回显
    get_bank_list: `${o}/${projectName}/bank_Card/get_bank_list`, // 银行卡列表
    change_card: `${o}/${projectName}/bank_Card/change_card`, // 换卡
    bind_card: `${o}/${projectName}/bank_Card/bind_card`, // 绑卡
    send_bind_card_sms: `${o}/${projectName}/bank_Card/send_bind_card_sms`, // 获取绑卡验证码

    // 支付协议
    query_protocol_sign: `${o}/${projectName}/app/bankcard/query_protocol_sign`, // 查询是否签约过 [loan_applciation]
    protocol_sign: `${o}/${projectName}/app/bankcard/protocol_sign`, // 获取验证码 [protocol_auth]
    confirm_protocol_sign: `${o}/${projectName}/app/bankcard/confirm_protocol_sign`, // 签约 [protocol_auth]

    // paying
    get_pay_page: `${o}/${projectName}/app/loan/get_pay_page`, // [paying] 支付页数据接口
    generate_order: `${o}/${projectName}/app/vipcard/generate_order`, // [paying] 生成会员卡订单
    quick_pay: `${o}/${projectName}/app/loan/quick_pay`, // [paying] 快捷支付接口
    get_pay_status: `${o}/${projectName}/app/loan/get_pay_status`, // [pay_result] 查询支付结果
    get_available_coupon: `${o}/${projectName}/app/basic/get_available_coupon`, // [redpackets] 获取用户可用优惠券

    // found
    credit_score: `${o}/${projectName}/app/credit/credit_score`, // [found] 发现

    // sign
    sign_basic_info: `${o}/${projectName}/app/loan/sign_basic_info`, // [sign] 获取签约信息
    sign: `${o}/${projectName}/auth/sign`, // [sign] 签约确认接口

    // repay
    get_user_repay_detail: `${o}/${projectName}/app/loan/get_user_repay_detail`, // [repay] 还款详情
    // loan_market 贷款超市
    get_market_infos: `${o}/${projectName}/app/market/get_market_business_info`, // 获取超市详情
    get_market_banners: `${o}/${projectName}/app/market/get_market_banners`, // 获取贷超banner详情

    // 红包
    get_coupon_list: `${o}/${projectName}/coupon/get_coupon_list`, // 签约红包列表
    get_my_coupon_list: `${o}/${projectName}/coupon/get_my_coupon_list`, // 我的红包列表
    // 20181225 需求：身份信息确认
    ocr_confirm: `${o}/${projectName}/faceid/ocr_confirm` // 身份信息确认 verify/index
  }
  return path
}
